  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/transportation/\" rel=\"tag\">交通相关</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/03/06/mercedes-wants-to-bring-carplay-to-older-vehicles-this-year/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/c87f713e0c3c5d624467f3a1207666c1/carplay-mercedes-benz.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nApple 刚刚推出的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/CarPlay/\">CarPlay</a> 可能对很多车主来说很吸引，不过目前其中一个限制就是它目前只会在某几间车厂的新车上出现。而 Mercedes-Benz 最近就告诉了 9to5Mac，表示他们有计划为型号较旧的车推出一个「售后解决方案」，并在 2014 年完结之前推出。现时他们没有详细解说这个计划会如何实行，也当然没有指出当中会不会涉及任何改装或是收费。不知道其他厂商会不会有类似的计划呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/06/mercedes-wants-to-bring-carplay-to-older-vehicles-this-year/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://9to5mac.com/2014/03/06/mercedes-benz-working-on-aftermarket-carplay-installations-for-older-vehicles/\">9to5Mac</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/07/mercedes-wants-to-bring-carplay-to-older-vehicles-this-year/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20844819/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/07/mercedes-wants-to-bring-carplay-to-older-vehicles-this-year/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
